             was indicted for <rs id="t18070701-20-off123" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18070701-20-off123" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18070701-20-off123" type="offenceSubcategory" value="shoplifting"></interp>
               feloniously stealing on the <rs id="t18070701-20-cd124" type="crimeDate">9th of June</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18070701-20-off123 t18070701-20-cd124"></join>, a shawl, value 10 s. the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18070701-20-victim259" type="victimName">
                           George 
                           Hammond
                        <interp inst="t18070701-20-victim259" type="surname" value="Hammond"></interp>
